          <updateDate>2017-11-09T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Missed Opportunities in Education Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Education (ED) to report annually on grants not awarded under each of its competitive or discretionary grant programs. For each program, ED must publish a report on the 10 applications that were not funded (completely or partially), but showed the greatest potential to improve education in the United States. </p>]]></text>
          <actionDate>2017-11-09</actionDate>
        </item>
